'''Onderonian warbeast transports''' were a type of small [[Transport/Legends|transport]] craft that were used during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]] to shuttle [[drexl]] beasts to engage in battle on other [[Planet/Legends|worlds]], such as [[Cinnagar/Legends|Cinnagar]].

